rd Candidate\u202fC**, pending any additional information you might have\u2014especially regarding:\n- Any evidence of Candidate\u202fA\u2019s reliability or track record in safety\u2011critical situations.\n- Any details on Candidate\u202fD\u2019s teamwork or crew\u2011cooperation performance.\nIf anyone can fill those gaps, it would help confirm or adjust the assessment.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
